val parquetFileOfferTemp = sqlContext.read.parquet("/data/sidana/purch_april_2018/purch/2018-05-02T00-30-07UTC_sanitized.parquet/*.parquet")
val inputFile = parquetFileOfferTemp.filter(to_date($"utcDate")>="2018-04-01"&&to_date($"utcDate")<="2018-04-30")
inputFile.count
val goodUsers = inputFile.filter($"wasClicked").select($"userId".as("goodUserId")).distinct
val data = inputFile.join(goodUsers,inputFile("userId")===goodUsers("goodUserId")).drop(goodUsers("goodUserId"))
data.count

val parquetFileOfferTemp = sqlContext.read.parquet("/data/sidana/purch_april_2018/purch/2018-05-02T00-30-07UTC_sanitized.parquet/*.parquet")
val inputFile = parquetFileOfferTemp.filter(to_date($"utcDate")>="2018-04-01"&&to_date($"utcDate")<="2018-04-30").select("userId","keywords","wasClicked")
val goodUsers = inputFile.filter($"wasClicked").select($"userId".as("goodUserId")).distinct
val data = inputFile.join(goodUsers,inputFile("userId")===goodUsers("goodUserId")).drop(goodUsers("goodUserId"))
val keywds = data.select("keywords")
keywds.count
keywds.filter(!($"keywords").isNull).count

//display product_attributes

val parquetFileOfferTemp = sqlContext.read.parquet("/data/sidana/purch_april_2018/purch/2018-05-02T00-30-07UTC_sanitized.parquet/*.parquet")
val inputFile = parquetFileOfferTemp.filter(to_date($"utcDate")>="2018-04-01"&&to_date($"utcDate")<="2018-04-30").select("userId","keywords","productLemmas","wasClicked")
val goodUsers = inputFile.filter($"wasClicked").select($"userId".as("goodUserId")).distinct
val data = inputFile.join(goodUsers,inputFile("userId")===goodUsers("goodUserId")).drop(goodUsers("goodUserId"))
z.show(data)

//vocab of product lemmas

val parquetFileOfferTemp = sqlContext.read.parquet("/data/sidana/purch_april_2018/purch/2018-05-02T00-30-07UTC_sanitized.parquet/*.parquet")
val inputFile = parquetFileOfferTemp.filter(to_date($"utcDate")>="2018-04-01"&&to_date($"utcDate")<="2018-04-30").select("userId","productLemmas","wasClicked")
val goodUsers = inputFile.filter($"wasClicked").select($"userId".as("goodUserId")).distinct
val data = inputFile.join(goodUsers,inputFile("userId")===goodUsers("goodUserId")).drop(goodUsers("goodUserId"))

//data.count => sanity check 1,707,321

import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._

val productText = data.select("productLemmas")
val distinct_df = productText.withColumn("productLemmas", explode(col("productLemmas"))).
                     agg(collect_set("productLemmas").alias("distinct_productLemmas"))

distinct_df.select(size($"distinct_productLemmas").as("no_of_productLemmas")).show

// #of product lemmas out of total events non-null

// productText.count // #events sanity check 1,707,321
productText.filter(!($"productLemmas").isNull).count //#non-null events

// % of offers which have keywords length greater than 0
parquetFileOfferTemp.select("offerId").distinct.count
parquetFileOfferTemp.select("offerId","productLemmas").distinct.count

parquetFileOfferTemp.filter(size($"keywords")>0).select("offerid").distinct.count
